snippet.title: Helltaker Second Circle - Trailer
snippet.description:
I'm very excited to announce that I am working on this fan game as an animator! 
You can get the demo which is out right now via this link


https://helldev103120.itch.io/the-second-circle



My animations aren't done yet and will be implemented at a later date but you can support me and the rest of Team 133 by going to our itch page, or by donating to our PayPal link here:

https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_donations&business=547NT77FXDFGQ&item_name=Creating+The+Second+Circle%3A+A+HellTaker+Fan+Game&currency_code=USD

I thank you for your continued support in letting me do what I love for a living
